OL,3,C'Revolutionary' device to tackle acid
OL,4,Creflux given to first UK patients
OL,6,FThis can result in a range of symptoms
OL,7,Fincluding heartburn, regurgitation,
OL,8,Fdifficulty swallowing, bloating,
OL,9,Fexcessive salivation, coughing, nausea
OL,10,Fand a hoarse voice, as well as teeth
OL,11,Fand gum damage, nutritional problems,
OL,12,Fand sleep impairment.
OL,14,FRefluxStop is fixed to the upper part
OL,15,Fof the stomach wall and blocks
OL,16,Fmovement of the lower oesophageal
OL,17,Fsphincter to hold it in its original,
OL,18,Fnatural position and restore normal
OL,19,Fanatomy and function.
OL,1,W~k4~sj5j5~s1G                    G3/8
