OL,3,C'Revolutionary' device to tackle acid
OL,4,Creflux given to first UK patients
OL,6,FMade out of medical grade rounded
OL,7,Fsolid silicone, the implant measures
OL,8,Faround 25mm ` smaller than a ping pong
OL,9,Fball ` and is fitted via robotic-
OL,10,Fassisted laparoscopic (keyhole)
OL,11,Fsurgery as a day case, with patients
OL,12,Fin theatre for less than two hours.
OL,14,FA UHS spokeswoman said that
OL,15,Fapproximately 20% of the adult UK
OL,16,Fpopulation have problems with severe
OL,17,Facid reflux or GORD and UHS treats
OL,18,Fabout 50 patients every year with the
OL,19,Fcondition.
