OL,6,FFergus Noble, consultant general and
OL,7,Foesophagogastric surgeon at UHS, said:
OL,8,F"RefluxStop is revolutionary in that
OL,9,Fit is minimally invasive, restores the
OL,10,Flower oesophageal valve to its natural
OL,11,Fposition with no side effects and
OL,12,Foffers some patients a viable
OL,13,Ftreatment option for the first time."
